ensure python is installed (sudo apt install python3.8 )
ensure pip is installed (sudo apt install python-pip or sudo apt install python3-pip)
pip install xmlrunner
pip install unittest2 (or unittest3)
Freestyle job 
  - source: git
  - Build step: executes shell - python runtests.py (or your python file)
  - Post-build step: Publish Junit test report: sudo apt install python-pip
